        • discoveryTechnologies

          DiscoveryTechnology[] discoveryTechnologies
          This is the list of technologies used to discover elements in the net. The default is using SNMP first (trying v2 with a community string preference list first). If that should fail a try with V3 and if that should fail try with v1. These following options would have to be specifically enabled by the user. After this try ICMP and if ICMP is successful then SSH/CLI. Puppet.

        • serviceElementTypeExclusions

          edu.harvard.integer.common.topology.ServiceElementType[] serviceElementTypeExclusions
